**vi Editor**:
vimtutor -> help regarding vim commands.
vi <filename> -> To open the file in vi and modify it.

Command Mode to Input Mode(i/o/O/u):
Input Mode to Command Mode(esc):		

**Commands**:
:w -> write/save
:wq -> save and quit
:qa ->
Shift+g -> End of page
gg -> Top of Page
dd -> delete 1 line
8dd -> delete 8 line
u -> undo
yy -> copy 1 line
8yy -> Copy 8 lines
p -> Paste the copied
d -> cut

:%s/<word>/<replacement> -> replaces every single occurence in each line
:%s/<word>/<replacement>/g -> replaces all occurences.
